imdb.plot outline: In Relocation Relocation Australia property experts Bryce Holdaway and Veronica Morgan will set out to find the right properties for people who are looking to move house and want a change of scenery; on the hunt for a new home and new business premises; downsizing to help their kids get on the property ladder; or just seizing the moment to relocate to a place they never thought possible.
imdb.title: Relocation Relocation Australia
